{
  "stem": "10181.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they told you by certain hour, you have to be there, and then you go from there to there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So people complied and some of the people didn't comply.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But they didn't stay.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They-- they went into hiding, some people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My uncle could have gone into hiding.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He had the opportunity through my-- through his brothers, through my-- through Adolf, I'm sure.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I know that-- I know that for a fact that he had been in touch and had offered him a possibility, but I think he was afraid.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "His nerves-- I think his nerves were shot already.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was taking care of everybody, and I'm sure he must have had huge money problems, which I, of course, as a little child, didn't realize to take care of everybody but he did.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So and then of course, that-- that-- the nightly air raids didn't add to-- to-- to the-- to his comfort.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And everything was on his shoulders, so I don't think he had the nerves to-- to-- to go into hiding.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because you need those very strong nerves for that, too.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, when you went into hiding, you went to live in somebody's house usually.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You didn't go into a forest like you did in-- in some other areas.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Holland had no big forests anywhere.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You went to live in somebody's attic or somebody's cellar, and you couldn't move.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You were dependent on them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And usually it wasn't in the same-- usually, it was not in the same village where you lived, because it was much too dangerous.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because you know, there were some very-- even for the Dutch were not good to the Jews.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They should have been better, because most of the Jews were living with them for many generations.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
